content.section: Equestrian at the 2010 Summer Youth Olympics
content.content: The Equestrian competition at the 2010 Summer Youth Olympics in Singapore took place from August 18 to August 24 at the Singapore Turf Riding Club. There were two events, team jumping and individual jumping. The team jumping was between continents.
This table presents only individual results. Mixed team medals are not included.
